        <item>
            <title>新疆成全球最大单体光伏项目并网发电，电量可供 300 万户家庭使用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=worlds-largest-solar-plant</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:30:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[中国]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[全球最大单体光伏项目]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[新疆]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1241117</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">中国电力建设集团承建的新疆米东 3.5 吉瓦光伏项目第二标段工程于去年 8 月 29 日开始建设，早前宣布成功并网。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1241139 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-694x391.jpg" alt="世界最大单体光伏项目" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1241143 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-1-694x391.jpg" alt="世界最大单体光伏项目" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-1-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant-goes-online-in-china-2/">pv magazine International</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">米东 3.5 吉瓦光伏项目拼网后年发电量可达 60.9 亿 kWh，预计每年发电量足够 300 万户中国家庭使用，甚至能满足卢森堡、巴布亚新几内亚等小国整年的电力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1241144 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-2-694x391.jpg" alt="世界最大单体光伏项目" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-2-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cgdglargestpvfarminx-2.jpg 1052w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant-goes-online-in-china-2/">pv magazine International</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">这个全球最大单体光伏项目位于乌鲁木齐市米东区北部沙漠，占地约 20 万亩，装机容量为 3.5 吉瓦。米东 3.5 吉瓦光伏项目每年节约标准煤约 194.88 万吨，减少二氧化碳排放量约 607.17 万吨、烟尘约 165.65 万吨、氮氧化合物约 91350 吨，远远优胜于同等规模的燃煤电厂，对加快当地能源结构优化和推动电力市场建设起了积极的作用。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20240606/s00004/1717652898056/%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e5%96%ae%e9%ab%94%e5%85%89%e4%bc%8f%e9%a0%85%e7%9b%ae%e4%bd%b5%e7%b6%b2%e7%99%bc%e9%9b%bb-%e6%af%8f%e5%b9%b4%e7%99%bc%e9%9b%bb%e9%87%8f%e8%b6%b3%e5%a4%a0300%e8%90%ac%e6%88%b6%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR1SWsBFMVIxfF_sh8eEkd_w54L9_hO39-EaJrePrCV_0A5u45O1i4ny4c0_aem_ARGHmmcVNAwFsnUsiWk_GxESUk_OxzkJRfQrGOACGJMfHFzEOtWXgufc90n38pBQLO_xzCFMJ6d1NpFEgKhAYzTl">明报</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant-goes-online-in-china-2/">pv magazine International</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/drone-mainland-china/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】到中国玩航拍必知 10 件事，注册无人机 + 飞行高度距离 + 禁飞区 + 领牌制度</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/saudi-fund-invests-in-china-effort-to-create-rival-to-openai/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">沙特阿拉伯基金投资中国 AI　智谱 AI 获注资 4 亿美元</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/xi-bot/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国政府研发大模型应用　结合习近平思想作为知识库</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/06/worlds-largest-solar-plant/fun-tech/">新疆成全球最大单体光伏项目并网发电，电量可供 300 万户家庭使用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
